Cape Town - Level 3b water restrictions, the City of Cape Town s water red alert, have officially kicked in on Wednesday as dam levels continue to dip dangerously close to crisis point.The Cape Argus has developed a way to help you save water by cutting down your usage in the shower.&nbsp;To help keep your showers to a maximum of two-and-a-half minutes, they had Acoustic Element and Amy Tjasink write a song. Drip Drop (the Argus Shower Song) is exactly two-and-a-half minutes long.&nbsp;Watch the music video below.Cape Argus